<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3865029>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. The holotype of Eremias kakari sp. nov. PMNH 842: A—dorsal view; B—ventral view; C—dorsal head view; D—lateral head view." ;
