    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3865031>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Paratypes of Eremias kakari sp. nov. PMNH 840, 843–846 dorsal (above) and ventral (below) view." ;
